{"tid":2197804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SELL HK: 租務淨租金收入僅跌6%","createTime":"2020-09-11T01:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T01:52:06.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae5b9a3568cae8d90404c67c5096806f7840aa9","tid":2197804,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:45:00.000Z","msg":"疫情嚴重打擊經旅遊及零售業，惟新地去年總租金收入僅跌3.4%至242.14億元，淨租金收入則約185.65億元，按年跌5.7%。新地表示，自2至6月份共提供逾10億元租金寬減，佔集團去年度總租金收入約4%。內地租務方面，收入按年增長2.38%至41.66億元人民幣。電訊及運輸等業務的分部盈利分別跌36.8%及22%，至5.2億及13.65億元；酒店業務則轉盈為虧蝕約3.33億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20200911/s00004/1599761933722/%e6%96%b0%e5%9c%b0%e6%a0%b8%e5%bf%83%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%91%e4%b8%80%e6%88%90-%e9%83%ad%e7%82%b3%e8%81%af-%e5%89%8d%e6%99%af%e4%b8%8d%e7%a2%ba%e5%ae%9a-%e9%82%84%e7%9c%8b%e7%96%ab%e6%83%85%e7%99%bc%e5%b1%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20200911%2Fs00004%2F1599761933722%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%259c%25b0%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e5%25bf%2583%25e7%259b%2588%25e5%2588%25a9%25e8%25b7%258c%25e8%25bf%2591%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%2590-%25e9%2583%25ad%25e7%2582%25b3%25e8%2581%25af-%25e5%2589%258d%25e6%2599%25af%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a-%25e9%2582%2584%25e7%259c%258b%25e7%2596%25ab%25e6%2583%2585%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%25b1%2595&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=179ded93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20200911%2Fs00004%2F1599761933722%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%259c%25b0%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e5%25bf%2583%25e7%259b%2588%25e5%2588%25a9%25e8%25b7%258c%25e8%25bf%2591%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%2590-%25e9%2583%25ad%25e7%2582%25b3%25e8%2581%25af-%25e5%2589%258d%25e6%2599%25af%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a-%25e9%2582%2584%25e7%259c%258b%25e7%2596%25ab%25e6%2583%2585%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%25b